            "circlet_of_logos": {
              "desc": "<p>琥珀金打的耳饰，其上镶嵌着宝石，闪烁着奇妙的光芒。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/07/36540823/999a78b73235c08ca4a0664a23e7079f_2530953698871693504.png",
