            },
            "goblet_of_eonothem": {
              "desc": "<p>一尊古老的金杯，形制奇妙华丽，空空如也的<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">腹内回响着呢喃之声。</span></p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/07/36540823/0c319d4054751adc08be47eee0ebad53_5383093074825252734.png",
              "id": "artifact47293",
